## Root Directory Pages

- **/briefs** — All legal briefs and pleadings
- **/appendix** — Supporting appendices
- **/addendum** — Additional materials
- **/oa** — Opening arguments and oral argument materials
- **/orders** — Court orders and proposed orders
- **/kits** — Reusable templates and relief banks
- **/release** — Public release materials
- **/archive** — Complete case archive

## Root Files (Dashboard/Index Pages)

- Master Index — Central navigation hub
- Start Here — Workspace landing page with instructions
- Changelog — Track updates and revisions
- Checksums — Document verification tracking

## Archive Structure

- **/Public** — Exhibits (PDF-A with Bates), Index (CSV + JSON), Summaries
- **/Restricted** — Unredacted materials and work product
- **/Press_Kit** — OnePager.pdf, Timeline.png, Top10_Exhibits.pdf

**Case Archive Subfolders:**

- 00_Timeline
- 01_Pleadings
- 02_Exhibits (with Bates numbering)
- 03_Orders
- 04_Notices
- 05_FOIA

This structure makes collaboration scalable and ensures everything is portable and verifiable.